ActEmployment Insurance Act
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (Fishing) REGULATIONS which will amend the Maximum Insurable Earnings (MIE) provision of the Employment Insurance (Fishing) Regulations by linking it back to the one prescribed in the Employment Insurance (EI) Act, in order to reconcile a technical discrepancy. The Regulations come into force on March 29, 2009.
